Date: 24th Jan 2016
Time: 17:15 to 18:00

Ski Sunday comes from Kitzbuhel in Austria, home of the classic World Cup downhill. Raced over the infamous Streif, winning here guarantees legendary status. There are also highlights of the women's downhill from Cortina, and Jenny Jones meets the girl who beat her to Olympic gold in 2014 - the queen of snowboarding, Jamie Anderson.
